<h6><strong style="background-color: transparent;">1) Leave Tracking &amp; Absence Management Software anywhere, any time on any device</strong></h6>
<p>e-days brings a sense of accessibility to your leave tracking &amp; absence management processes, one not previously felt by restrictive paper and spreadsheets only accessible by management. With employees able to access their allowances and existing holiday in real time, the amount of &lsquo;how much holiday do I have left&rsquo; emails are reduced to zero.</p>
<p>Our Leave Tracking &amp; Absence Management software is accessible on any device, anywhere at any time as long as you&rsquo;re connected to the internet.</p>
<p><a href="/contact#demo" class="button button_action">Book demo</a></p>


