<h6><strong>2) Integration with or sitting alongside existing HRIS</strong></h6>
<p>We understand that many businesses will already have an existing HR System in place, the problem is these systems don&rsquo;t always focus on Absence Management. That&rsquo;s why we made Absence Management software our specialism and made it as easy as possible to integrate into or even sit alongside your existing HR system.</p>
<p>We&rsquo;ve successfully integrated e-days with ADP, SAP, Workday and many more, allowing clients to create a complete HR solution for their organisation.</p>
<p><a href="/contact#demo" class="button button_action">Book demo</a></p>


</div>
    
