<h6><strong>3) Money Saving Solution</strong></h6>
<p>Let&rsquo;s be honest, when it comes to scoping out new technologies for your organisation, the main aim is going to be delivering cost savings to your existing HR processes. You can find out exactly how much you could save with e-days <a href="/Savings-calculator">HERE</a>.</p>
<p>e-days saves organisations both time and money, take a second to think about how long a request for annual leave takes you to process from start to finish. 10 minutes? e-days will cut that time down to just seconds, with a request sent and approval granted in just a couple of clicks.</p>
